ReadMe

Drill ID = JD_2026_06_W1_CampusLostAndFound

Class Name: CampusLostAndFoundApp

Difficulty: Level 2 — Multi-Class Application

Estimated Time: 45–60 minutes

Actual Time Taken: 47 minutes

Written by: Chanwoo Park

Problem
Create a campus lost-and-found program that manages lost items, searches by keyword,
updates claim status, and counts unclaimed items.

Requirements
- Use at least 3 classes.
- Store multiple LostItem objects in an array.
- Search by item name or found location.
- Mark an item as claimed by owner name.
- Count remaining unclaimed items.

Learning Objective
Practice object collaboration, array traversal, String comparison, conditional logic,
and object state updates.
